## Setup

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://github.com/jeevankhatri001/Mlops-cifar-10.git
cd Mlops-cifar-10

# Environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Start services
docker compose up -d

# Run ingestion
python -m app.ingestion.ingest

# Start MLflow
mlflow server --host 0.0.0.0 --port 5000 --backend-store-uri sqlite:///mlflow.db --default-artifact-root ./mlruns &

# Train
python -m app.training.train

# Start API
uvicorn app.api.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000 &

# Start frontend
streamlit run streamlit_app.py --server.port 8501 --server.address 0.0.0.0
```

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions runs on every push to `main`:
1. **Lint** — flake8 on `app/` directory
2. **Test** — pytest smoke tests (model import, forward pass, parameter count, API import)
3. **Docker build** — validates Docker Compose configuration
